Templates for CommentPlugin - See CommentPlugin#Customisation for help

---------------------------------------------------------------------------
Templates used in rest of file

Generic prompt box used by other templates
%TMPL:DEF{promptbox}%
<table>
 <tr valign="middle">
  <td>
   <textarea %DISABLED% rows=3 cols=50 name="comment" wrap="soft">%MESSAGE%</textarea>
  </td>
  <td>
   <input %DISABLED% type="submit" value="Add comment" />
  </td>
 </tr>
</table>
%TMPL:END%

Short comment, signed and dated
%TMPL:DEF{outputoneliner}%
%URLPARAM{"comment"}% -- %WIKIUSERNAME% - %SERVERTIME%
%TMPL:END%

